name: Chokk (V)
Lore: 'Klatooinian bodyguard currently in the paid service of Jabba the Hutt. Chokk takes pride in his work, and he is very good at it.',
Text: 'Deploys -1 to Tatooine. While with your non-droid character, if a battle was just initiated here, may use 1 Force to place Chokk in Used Pile; Interrupts may not be played until the weapons segment ends.(Original concept by Greg Shaw - Coruscant Regionals 2004)',
